<doc id="898327" wikidata="Q6030427" url="?curid=898327" title="Info Wars (film)">
<text>Info Wars (styled as info wars) is a 2004 documentary film about the mechanics of modern information warfare and media hacking. It shows some of the ways special interests manipulate modern mass media to reach their ends. It explains the ways the flow of mass media could turn the tide in any battle, real or online.

The film is named after InfoWars, launched in 1999.

