<doc id="898396" wikidata="Q5561876" url="?curid=898396" title="Gill, Texas">
<text>Gill is a rural unincorporated community in south central Harrison County, Texas, United States. The community is six miles south of the county seat, Marshall, on U.S. Route 59.

